{"tid":1532710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金屬氦氣球變鐵路炸彈","createTime":"2019-09-02T15:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T14:38:35.000Z","uid":238343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"355aa66beb44005913e9619228dcb436b7903c7f","tid":1532710,"uid":238343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:01:32.000Z","msg":"舊聞一則，唔好學！<br />\n<br />\n金屬氦氣球玩具隨時變成鐵路炸彈。氦氣球會影響電纜運作，被港鐵列為違禁品，以往港鐵職員發現乘客持氦氣球進入港鐵範圍會即時沒收。但本報發現，近月港鐵職員防備鬆懈，乘客攜帶氦氣球入閘視而不見，鐵路範圍處處見到「鐵路炸彈」。專家警告，如氦氣球飄起觸到鐵路電纜，會引致電力短路，可能會引起小火，導致電力供應系統「跳掣」，引發交通大災難。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140203/00410_097.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140203%2F00410_097.html&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1apgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=5d233a60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140203/00410_097.html</a>"},{"pid":"2c37cee5a866951935690409bdaf03c504e02566","tid":1532710,"uid":300690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:03:20.000Z","msg":"地鐵太多人 真心唔推"},{"pid":"3c7689ac85408af5069dd243521d3fdb53020941","tid":1532710,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:05:46.000Z","msg":"咪撚整傷自己人<br />\n對準政權啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵職員<br />\n今日你包庇唔交CCTV<br />\n他日你自己必定遭殃</span></strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">譴責黨鐵 黑箱作業<br />\n放警入閘 狂毆乘客</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a9acf31c13418b01bf7a16543f2b7bf46cf88fbc","tid":1532710,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:09:19.000Z","msg":"下次有恐襲 記得拉消防制"},{"pid":"5a74fa7f885c6f89167c05fc6fb055012621a896","tid":1532710,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0